title: She Must Burn - Under The Shadows (EP) 2015 ak
description:
She Must Burn "Under The Shadows (EP)" (2015)

Technical blackened metallic guitars, symphonic synths and a barrage of blastbeats form an unrelenting foundation for the twin vocals of hellish screamer Joseph Louis Sinclair and angelic vocalist/keyboardist Aimy Miller. 
A powerful layered texture reminiscent of Bleeding Through, Deadlock, Abigail Williams and even Behemoth at times, the band juxtapose the chilling evil of early black metal with powerful soaring melodies. 	

Deathcore, Symphonic Metal
